{"id":244640,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-维权人士赵振甲劳教起诉被法院不开庭驳/","date":"2012-08-02T09:16:08Z","modified":"2012-08-02T09:16:08Z","title":"维权网 | 维权人士赵振甲劳教起诉被法院不开庭驳回(图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<p>（维权网信息员蒋理、甘苦报道）今天（8月2日）本网信息员获悉，辽宁维权人士赵振甲被劳教而提起诉讼一案，于昨天已经被北京市西城区人民法院，在不开庭审理情况下，作出驳回起诉裁定。</p>\n<p>据赵振甲的代理律师北京莫少平律师事务所律师马纲权说：“赵振甲现被羁押于辽宁省朝阳市劳教所，7月份的时候，法官告诉我们准备不把赵振甲从朝阳市劳教所带回北京来参加庭审，只让我们代理人参加庭审，但我们坚决不同意，没想到法院就直接下裁定驳回起诉了。”</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-utMoKuEnfLA/UBo2UVn1tEI/AAAAAAAAKiE/tACgDGwwb1g/s1600/%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A61.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-utMoKuEnfLA/UBo2UVn1tEI/AAAAAAAAKiE/tACgDGwwb1g/s320/%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A61.JPG\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-QpWt53U0OGw/UBo3mlIrv7I/AAAAAAAAKiM/UUrHSx8XWWw/s1600/%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A62.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-QpWt53U0OGw/UBo3mlIrv7I/AAAAAAAAKiM/UUrHSx8XWWw/s320/%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%A62.JPG\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7612919886193301807?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","a